data.description: FANTASTIC opportunity to own in the perfect Brookline LOCATION! NEWLY REMODELED, bright one bedroom with DEEDED PARKING. The new, modern kitchen boasts quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, under cabinet lighting, and a pantry. Adjacent to the kitchen is the sun-filled living room and bonus space, perfect for a home office. Fall in love with the new hardwood floors that flow throughout. In the bedroom, you will find large windows and generous closet with custom closet system. Finally, a tastefully done bathroom and linen closet. In addition to on-site management, ownership comes with access to basement storage areas and limited use of the Brook House pool. You cannot beat the LOCATION as this unit is close to Brookline Village, the D and E lines, multiple bus lines, and the Longwood Medical area. Enjoy a break from the city with the walking/biking paths of Leverett pond and the Emerald Necklace just around the corner. DO NOT MISS THIS RARE FIND. Open house: May 21st 12-3pm
